OL,3,CReward offered after monkey abandoned
OL,4,Con London bus
OL,6,FA reward of up to #3,000 is being
OL,7,Foffered for information leading to any
OL,8,Farrest and conviction after a monkey
OL,9,Fwas abandoned on a London bus.
OL,11,FThe female common marmoset was
OL,12,Fdiscovered on a 302 bus waiting in
OL,13,FKensal Rise, north-west London, on
OL,14,FFriday.
OL,16,FA mother had been unable to move her
OL,17,Fbuggy down the bus aisle because a
OL,18,Flaundry bag was sticking out of the
OL,19,Fluggage bay.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/4
