PN,37102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1784843301
OL,3,CReward offered after monkey abandoned
OL,4,Con London bus
OL,6,FWhen the bus driver pushed the bag out
OL,7,Fof the way, the monkey ` since named
OL,8,FOyster ` started "chirping and
OL,9,Fjumping".
OL,11,FOyster has been checked by a vet and
OL,12,Frehomed at a sanctuary.
OL,14,FAnimal charity Peta is offering the
OL,15,Freward in a bid to find whoever
OL,16,Fabandoned her.
OL,26,@pD@ROUqD@HO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/4
