PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1784843301
OL,3,CReward offered after monkey abandoned
OL,4,Con London bus
OL,6,FPeta vice-president of programmes
OL,7,FElisa Allen said: "We're calling on
OL,8,Fanyone with information about this
OL,9,Fcase to come forward so that whoever
OL,10,Fabandoned Oyster can be held
OL,11,Faccountable before endangering anyone
OL,12,Felse.
OL,14,F"Abandoning an animal is an
OL,15,Fextraordinary betrayal. This monkey
OL,16,Fdeserved care and protection, not to
OL,17,Fbe discarded like rubbish."
OL,26,@oD@SOUvD@AOUyD@[O]
