OL,3,CReward offered after monkey abandoned
OL,4,Con London bus
OL,6,FIt is feared to be the "first of many"
OL,7,Fabandonments after April's new
OL,8,Flegislation mandated that all primates
OL,9,Fkept in England are licensed, the
OL,10,FRSPCA said.
